description: A network of over 8,000 dentists across Australia offering reduced out-of-pocket costs for members. Participating dentists agree to charge within set fee schedules for common dental services.
member_benefit: No gap on preventive dental services including check-ups, scale and clean, and standard x-rays at participating dentists

description: National network of optical retailers and independent optometrists providing quality eyewear and eye care services at agreed prices for fund members.
member_benefit: Up to 30% discount on frames and lenses, plus no gap on standard single vision lenses with participating providers

description: Extensive network of physiotherapy clinics committed to providing quality care with reduced out-of-pocket expenses for members across metropolitan and regional areas.
member_benefit: Reduced gap payments on initial consultations and standard physiotherapy treatments at network providers

description: Agreements with private hospitals across Australia ensuring members receive quality hospital care with known costs. Includes major hospital groups such as Ramsay, Healthscope, and St Vincent's.
member_benefit: No or reduced excess on hospital admissions, access to single rooms where available, and known out-of-pocket costs

description: Participating medical specialists who agree to charge within the fund's gap cover schedule, reducing or eliminating out-of-pocket costs for in-hospital medical services.
member_benefit: No gap or known gap for in-hospital medical services when treated by participating specialists

description: Network of qualified chiropractors offering spinal and musculoskeletal treatments with agreed fee schedules for fund members seeking alternative therapies.
member_benefit: Reduced gap on initial and subsequent chiropractic consultations at participating practices

description: Premium dental network offering extended services including orthodontics, implants, and cosmetic dentistry at negotiated rates with specialist dental providers.
member_benefit: Discounted rates on major dental work including crowns, bridges, and orthodontic treatments at participating specialists

description: Network of regional and rural private hospitals ensuring members in country areas have access to quality hospital care close to home.
member_benefit: Access to private hospital care in regional areas with no gap on accommodation and theatre fees
